<plot>The makers of this comedy took the Frank Capra masterpiece, _It's a Wonderful Life (1946)_ (qv) and re-edited it and totally re-did the dialogue and sound effects. For example, in this version, the druggist Mr. Gower, sells cocaine to the Baily family; the hero, George Bailey, is sick of doing the Wonderful Life film and wants to star in action films; his brother, Harry, has a drug addiction and is trying to jump Annie the maid.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?181421</url></doc>
